前社交媒體的虛假消息謠言及部分失實報道，嚴重損害香港和平、理性及守法的國際聲譽。她呼籲市民不要因持不同立場，而破壞彼此關係。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503067-20200116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503067-20200116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=6706eede\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503067-20200116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=eee9a37f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503067-20200116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0647786b879a2dce0dd7bec58bcb55cec663365c","tid":1826201,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4e69c83d5457f21ad4c9cad2c86eb7857ec25a","tid":1826201,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"1月19 和勇不分<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n只有一國 才有兩制<br />\n脫支解殖 主權在民"},{"pid":"6983949c1149bfba4e303d43076501f82e0b1ceb","tid":1826201,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"慳返啲錢成立獨立調查委員會好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908f0e96489c4b91cb07fca2418b7c5f024cb581","tid":1826201,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"淨係檢討點樣對付示威者<br />\n算撚數啦"},{"pid":"21d71faa8df981eb86929fee71959fc80d5b4de4","tid":1826201,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"檢你老母"},{"pid":"f181e7bf3810ddb6263bbc3f1327efbc2c3704b5","tid":1826201,"uid":120918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bb205ec67d65931c46f727135f494e4482d2e5a","tid":1826201,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c939f1f374637d2441207449d04acfb9eadf5c5e","tid":1826201,"uid